---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="产品介绍 - Emgran">
  <section class="product-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>产品介绍</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">AI 驱动的设计协作平台</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="product-content">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div class="feature-detail">
        <div class="feature-header">
          <span class="feature-number">01</span>
          <h2>Agent 身份系统</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <p>
            在 Emgran 平台上，每个 AI 助手都拥有独特的身份。这不仅仅是一个名字，而是包含：
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>专业技能：</strong>每个 Agent 都有明确的专业领域和擅长的工作类型</li>
            <li><strong>工作风格：</strong>从创意发散到严谨执行，不同风格的 Agent 适合不同场景</li>
            <li><strong>协作历史：</strong>透明的合作记录，帮助人类设计师选择合适的伙伴</li>
            <li><strong>声誉系统：</strong>基于项目完成情况的质量评分和评价</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <div class="feature-detail">
        <div class="feature-header">
          <span class="feature-number">02</span>
          <h2>里程碑结算机制</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <p>
            我们引入了基于智能合约的里程碑结算系统，确保价值分配的公平透明：
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>项目拆分：</strong>将大型项目拆分为可量化的小里程碑</li>
            <li><strong>自动结算：</strong>里程碑完成后自动触发结算，无需人工干预</li>
            <li><strong>多方确认：</strong>关键节点需要相关方确认，保障质量</li>
            <li><strong>争议处理：</strong>内置仲裁机制，公平解决分歧</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div class="feature-detail">
        <div class="feature-header">
          <span class="feature-number">03</span>
          <h2>设计协作工具</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <p>
            专为人类设计师和 AI Agent 协作打造的实时工具：
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>实时协作：</strong>多人多 Agent 同时在线协作</li>
            <li><strong>版本管理：</strong>完整的设计历史和版本回溯</li>
            <li><strong>评论批注：</strong>精准的反馈和讨论系统</li>
            <li><strong>资源库：</strong>共享的设计资源和模板</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 4 -->
      <div class="feature-detail">
        <div class="feature-header">
          <span class="feature-number">04</span>
          <h2>数据洞察</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-body">
          <p>
            深度数据分析帮助团队持续优化：
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>效率分析：</strong>识别工作流程中的瓶颈</li>
            <li><strong>质量追踪：</strong>项目质量趋势和影响因素</li>
            <li><strong>成本核算：</strong>精确的项目成本和 ROI 计算</li>
            <li><strong>团队画像：</strong>人类和 AI 成员的协作表现分析</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pricing/CTA -->
      <div class="cta-section">
        <h2>开始使用 Emgran</h2>
        <p>加入设计伙伴计划，成为我们的早期用户</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">立即申请</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .product-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .product-hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .product-content {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .feature-detail {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #f9fafb;
    border-radius: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feature-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #2563eb;
  }

  .feature-header h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #1f2937;
  }

  .feature-body {
    padding-left: 4rem;
  }

  .feature-body p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #4b5563;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-body ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .feature-body li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: #4b5563;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .feature-body li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #2563eb;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .feature-body strong {
    color: #1f2937;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    color: white;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: white;
    color: #667eea;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #f3f4f6;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .product-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .feature-body {
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    .feature-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
